Long-term cost-effectiveness of Oncotype DX® versus current clinical practice 
from a Dutch cost perspective.

Kip M(1)(2), Monteban H(3), Steuten L(1)(4).

Author information:
(1)Panaxea BV, Health Economics & Reimbursement, Enschede, The Netherlands.
(2)Department of Health Technology & Services Research, University of Twente, 
